
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 04 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Luxation' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Posteroradial' radio button is enabled
And 'Posterior' radio button is enabled
And 'Ulnar' radio button is enabled
And 'Anterior' radio button is enabled
And 'Divergent' radio button is enabled
And 'Status post' checkbox is enabled

And 'Terrible triad of the elbow' radio button is enabled
And 'Monteggia-like lesion' radio button is enabled
And 'Essex-Lopresti lesion' radio button is enabled
And 'Monteggia fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Status post' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Monteggia fracture' radio button
Then 'Type A/I' radio button is enabled
And 'Type B/II' radio button is enabled
And 'Type C/III' radio button is enabled
And 'Type D/IV' radio button is enabled
